<ab facs="#facs_205_r1l27">ʒum Stein gefürt ſey / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan></del></ab>
<pb facs="#facs_206" id="102r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_206_r1l1"><expan>beſtell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd daran ſeın wellet vmb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_206_r1l2"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> armman ledıg <expan>gelaſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd ſeın hab <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> . als </ab>
