</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_205" id="101v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Heymramb <expan>Hasling<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        zum Stein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Hasling<ex>er</ex></expan>, uns hat furbracht
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und ratgesell Hanns Tucher der
                                <expan>elt<ex>er</ex></expan>, wie sein
                            <expan>hint<ex>er</ex>sess</expan> Hanns <expan>Mülln<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        auf seinr mül zu Rotawrach, die er besecz und entsecz und mit tür und tor
                        besliess, <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan>, etwievil seinr hab
                                <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> und hinein zum Stein gefürt sey.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir <pb facs="#facs_206" id="102r"/>
<expan>bestell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und daran sein wellet umb
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> armman ledig
                            <expan>gelass<ex>en</ex></expan> und sein hab
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. Als etc. Das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>o</ex>m<ex>ini</ex>ca</expan> die <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
                        Elisabeth.</ab>
</div>
